{"tid":2327084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"多倫多黃店【天網恢恢】大家好被噴油案 約克區以種族仇恨罪案正式展開調查","createTime":"2020-12-15T22:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T03:35:30.000Z","uid":190615,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1836d3b547edcf4c6232cf8c8125c3701dabb21e","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:29:43.000Z","msg":"烈治文山大家好慘遭噴油破壞的案件，約克區警方宣佈正式展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方公佈於2020年12月9日接獲一宗在社交媒體具侵略性貼文的事件。聲稱位於280 West Beaver Creek Road一家餐館貼上一張與疫情有關的海報。警方調查後發現餐館早已把海報移除。隨後於同日晚間7時至翌日早上10時，該餐館的門窗被油漆塗污，圖案惹人反感。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲如有任何目擊證人、閉路電視或汽車鏡頭拍攝到任何可疑的人物或情況，請儘快向警方提供資料。<br />\n<br />\n約克區警方稱不能容忍任何針對種族、族裔、語言、膚色、年齡、性別、宗教、性取向、精神或身體殘疾人士的仇恨犯罪，違者將被檢控並訴諸法律。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何人士能提供線索，請聯絡約克區仇恨罪行科，電話：1-866-876-5423內線7797，撲滅罪行熱線1-800-222-TIPS，<a href=\"http://或網上匿名報案www.1800222tips.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%96%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88www.1800222tips.com&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=113877ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">或網上匿名報案www.1800222tips.com</a>。"},{"pid":"d523aa3974352c3ce458fa184860e17ee74eb872","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:30:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.torontowhatsup.ca/%e5%a4%9a%e9%9d%a2%e7%9d%87/pepper_wok_vandalized_yrp_20201215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.torontowhatsup.ca%2F%25e5%25a4%259a%25e9%259d%25a2%25e7%259d%2587%2Fpepper_wok_vandalized_yrp_20201215%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=66838e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.torontowhatsup.ca/%e5%a4%9a%e9%9d%a2%e7%9d%87/pepper_wok_vandalized_yrp_20201215/</a>"},{"pid":"8848cd4f2ea3ef946e84760fdf6d0f93673a8331","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:31:29.000Z","msg":"小粉紅 顫抖吧!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7f676a0433b92831785b9752ed78ae38488f60","tid":2327084,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdca55e8660e923407ac3b290497283904bd9b3","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:35:18.000Z","msg":"英文警方公佈全文:<a href=\"https://www.yrp.ca/en/Modules/News/index.aspx?newsId=b25c158e-4feb-4578-b685-ef83d4d66375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yrp.ca%2Fen%2FModules%2FNews%2Findex.aspx%3FnewsId%3Db25c158e-4feb-4578-b685-ef83d4d66375&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=2ec35ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yrp.ca/en/Modules/News/index.aspx?newsId=b25c158e-4feb-4578-b685-ef83d4d66375</a><br />\n<br />\nInvestigators with the York Regional Police Hate Crime Unit are appealing for witnesses after a restaurant was vandalized in the City of Richmond Hill.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOn Wednesday, December 9, 2020, York Regional Police were contacted regarding offensive social media posts about a restaurant located at 280 West Beaver Creek Road. Further investigation revealed the restaurant had posted a sign in its window referencing the pandemic, which has since been removed. At some point between December 9, 2020, at 7 p.m. and December 10, 2020, at 10 a.m., the storefront of the restaurant was vandalized with spray paint.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nInvestigators are asking any witnesses, anyone with information or anyone with video surveillance footage in that area, to please come forward.<br />\n<br />\nYork Regional Police does not tolerate hate crime in any form. Those who victimize individuals based on race, national or ethnic origin, language, colour, religion, age, gender, sexual orientation, gender identity or mental or physical disability will be prosecuted to the fullest extent of the law.<br />\n<br />\nAnyone with information can contact the York Regional Police Hate Crime Unit at 1-866-876-5423, ext. 7797 or Crime Stoppers at 1-800-222-TIPS, leave an anonymous tip online at <a href=\"http://www.1800222tips.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1800222tips.com&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=3b9eab17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.1800222tips.com</a>."},{"pid":"4a7421c7378d331a44ba9b7df5b0f5c0d9f9ada6","tid":2327084,"uid":256837,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:35:53.000Z","msg":"如果唔係搵咗議員搞大咗件事，差佬都唔會重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312a2ddcb4c53763ff36ffea02525fd9edb8d96c","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"4a7421c7378d331a44ba9b7df5b0f5c0d9f9ada6","tid":2327084,"uid":256837,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:35:53.000Z","msg":"如果唔係搵咗議員搞大咗件事，差佬都唔會重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T22:41:51.000Z","msg":"依家起碼話比班支那人聽呢度係加拿大唔係支那, 唔鍾意 咁玻璃心嘅就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c755ff28a9ad6b53a1fd05b8990fd99653709c4","tid":2327084,"uid":190615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:01:39.000Z","msg":"通緝小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e753570e34a1b860ab3aabe90b2b32d38b64e58","tid":2327084,"uid":282347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T23:03:41.000Z","msg":"香港民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\